values: Ok so most of you reading this (to the best of my knowledge) are aware of what happened Friday night. Well as if it happening that once wasn't bad enough. We had to go and do it again. I have felt like shit since about 6ish this morning when Nick got up and walked out! All I wanna do is cry. Bryce and myself have talked and agreed that last night went to far and the way we treated Nick was all sorts of fucked up. We have agreed that for the best we are not going to allow this to happen again. We will remain friends and hang out, I am determined to kick his ass in Halo at least once! I am just so glad he is on the same page as me, now the hard part is going to be getting Nick to forgive us. That is all I really want, even if I never see Bryce again! I want Nick back. I just wanna talk to him and tell him how I feel, and that sadly means I would probably fess up that I have liked him for months and it just killed me to watch him get up and walk out. I would tell him that I do like him that means I should have never allowed anything to happen with Bryce. My only defense being that Nick just needs to understand how much I don't like myself these days and how low my self esteem has been and to have a cute guy throw himself at me it is really hard to say no, and I know that it hurt Nick in the process but my heart has been aching for two days now over it.

ok I don't even know where to begin...I am in a weird ass mood and all I wanna do is cry and tell people off. I just wanna start texting people and tell them how I really feel! And I know I shouldn't. I needed to talk so I texted one of the few people who I would still be up this time of night(Nick), only problem with that is that he is one of the people I would like to be honest with and kinda want to but don't want to at the same time. I want to tell him that I think he is hot and I like him and that I hate that he thinks my friend (that he doesn't even know) is hot...FUCK ME! I wanna fucking tell off Norm and tell him that they way he and his girlfriend treated me was all sorts of wrong and that I did not deserve it. That I am fucking glad he loves her and that is a damn good thing cuz neither of their fucking crazy asses would ever find anyone else to put of with their shit! Like I said they are both fucking crazy and I wanna tell Norm he might wanna learn to take grab of his own fucking balls and tell his girlfriend to fucking let go once in a while! Oh and then there is the fact that I recently found out that my first love is engaged to be married and his fucking girlfriend is fucking pregnant! I mean honestly are you shitting me? I bet I don't even fucking get invited to the wedding! And we used to talk about me wearing a tux and being in his line! Ha ha ha fuck that!
I am so fucking bored of my lazy ass bro and his nasty ass ways my house currently smell like someone ate something rancid puked it up and pissed in it! And when I tell him the house smells all he can fucking say is I know! I am about [  ] this close to cleaning up all my shit pack up some essentials and find someone to bum off of for a while and believe I can fucking find someone who will be willing to give up a couch! I hate living away from my mom! I miss her! I am glad that she is fucking happy but that makes only one of us! I am so not happy with my life! I am fat and only getting fatter! I work at a dead end job and I am having no luck finding a new fucking job that I will like, I used to fucking like my job and it has gone down the shitter since about thanksgiving! I want fucking out but I just can't bring myself to do it! I wanna take charge of my own life! I hate depending on others to fucking live...I am fucking 19 years old and with practically nothing to show for it! I have half-assed my entire life and I know it. That is not a fucking good feeling! I could just cry right now! This is not a good night for me to be alone I just realized...this is a dangerous time for me...I just don't what to fucking do and I haven't felt like shit runover twice in a long time and I do tonight! If you have read this far I am fucking amazed you stuck with it. I hope I did not make anyone uncomfortable with my swearing but is kinda how I feel...if you made it this far you fabulous and I love you for it. I think I will be done bitching now and no I don't feel any better so don't ask!

Alright so my last entry was vague and lame. Pretty much I made the decision that I wanted to clean up my life and that I was going to try and stop drinking and start going back to church. Ok well I have slowed down a LOT on the drinking but sad to say I have not put a complete stop to it. I have gone to church once and would also like to work on that one, but now that it is the new year I am not positive as to when it starts. I need to call someone and ask about that. 
I am also kinda surprised that I did not mention in my last entry the fact that my mother was getting married later that month, well she is married now and living in Orem. My house is a lonely one! and it is a damn good thing that my mom is my landlord or I would be living on the streets, in a a card board box. 
Ok so now that I got you caught up a little...
Today was a depressing day! OK so I have been depressed a lot of this week but today is kicking its ass. I don't know what to do with myself! I really just wanna pack up and move and quit my job and go start clean somewhere new. It is a good thing I am poor cuz I HONESTLY would probably do both of those things if it weren't for the money. I really would like a new Medical Assisting job, that is what I want to do but I really think a part of me is holding me back from really getting out and looking for a job because I fear that I am going to fail at it! I quit things before I can fail at them and I haven't decided what is worse, to quit or to fail? I really just wanna get my life together but I am not sure how I am going to do that.

Ok so Liz brought up live journal yesterday and I decided I really needed to come update mine. So here I am typing away but not sure what to say. I have many feelings going on right now and I am having a battle inside myself! I am not ready to talk about what it is yet, as much as I would love all of your input on the whole thing I think I just need to make this decision on my own and I know that it is going to be one of the hardest ones I ever make! I think I will lose some friends and some fun times but at the same time I know I will make new friends and I think I would be happier down the road...I just don't know!

Ok well on a completely different note I just got back from a 10 day vacation to Philly, PA. I stayed with some family out there. I won't lie to you, I was bored most of the time and wishing I were home but at the same time it was a nice break from the realities here at home. The reality of my home is not a happy one for me right now! It is hard for me to explain do to the fact that I am not sure I understand it all myself. 

Ok well I think I have rambled on sufficiently for today...

Ok so I am updating and not at work this time. You should all be proud of me! Ok so I finally think Logan is coming around...maybe. I just don't know! We were texting most of the night saturday and still didn't do anything (instead we spent the whole time trying to figure something out to do). So then I text him a couple of times Sunday with no response, so I am thinking I scared him off the night before. So I decide to just totally back off for a couple of days (but only a couple cuz we are going to the baseball game together on wednesday). So today was a half day for me at work, I got there at about noon, I ate lunch and had just sat down to start making call when I get a text. And what are the odds that it is from him? It says "whats up doc", so I am all happy that he text me first. His next text asked me when I got off of work (I am freakin happy now) so I ask him why, and his answer was not exactly what I was hoping for...basically he ran outta gas and was hoping for a ride. Oh man I was frustrated but because I wanted to see him I left work early to go and save his butt. It was ok I guess, we talked about stuff and things. He can't tell me that I can't find his house anymore. But even after I save his butt he didn't ask me to do anything tonight, and he knew I was doing nothing. I do know that I was the first person he asked to come save him, so he had to be thinking about me right? So what is your opinion? My grandma does not think that this is a good sign, but my mom does think it is a good thing. Logan is a shy, quiet guy and my mom thinks that I should be happy that is thought to ask me for help...I just don't know...any bright thoughts on the situation?

Ok so I was at HOSA (Health Occupation Students of America) Competition up in Layton this weekend, ok so thursday day to friday night. There was easily over a thousand students there and we were all staying in hotels up there for the one night. I was lame for the most part, but when we didn't have to be anywhere for our competition we were aloud to go anywhere we could walk to. So day one we went to opening ceremony strait off the bus (which was an hour of sitting there in our business attire not paying attention and clapping when everyone else did). So when that got done we all went and got our rooms, so me and my "roommates" for the night scored! we got a suite like our teachers and know one else did, our teachers didn't even know that we did until we told them. So we were probably the only room that didn't have to share beds (due to having a couch). So most of us had to go taken the written test portion of the competition at 4, so when we got done with that we all went out to dinner and walked to the mall. At the mall I bought blue fuzzy flip flops and my snotty/bitchy Juan Diego roommate told me if I bought them and wore them she would lock me out of the room, I bought them anyway and told her I would do what I wanted. We were going to go to a movie but the same girl decided we were going to have an O.C. party instead and all sit around in complete silence (unless she was talking) for an hour. My other roommate wouldn't shut up and she is one of the people that always has to "1up" your stories...hers is always worse. So at about midnight I put on my headphones and rolled over and went to sleep. So the next morning I get up and go down stairs for breakfast and eat all alone. I went back up stairs and showered and got all dressed up in my scrubs and lab coat and headed over to my personal competition. I didn't study at all so I was pretty sure I was fucked! So as everyone before me came out (I was last to go) they said it wasn't too bad but af course couldn't tell me what it was. So I went in, and the stuff I had to do was easy enough, a blood draw on a fake arm and a throat culture and agar plate, but of course I fuck things up cuz I have a judge breathing down my neck and everyone feels like an idiot talking to an arm, so I move on to the throat culture and agar plate where there is a different judge (I liked this guy better) so I did my thing and walked out. I was glad it was over and I had the next 3 hours to go do whatever the hell I want, which turned out to not be a whole lot. Went to closing ceremony and sat through everyones name that got 1st 2cd 3rd and then the top ten of every category. Well we finally made it to me and I tied for 5th out of 13 people, so I guess it could have been worse, especially without studying. So that was that, we got on the bus and went home. 
I must say if you have read all this shit you must have been hoping for something good or juicy well I am sorry to disappoint you either that or you are one bored fuck and for that I am also sorry. 

MUAH ~ Jen

In your eyes, people can't seem to see anything
because your eyes are covered up by tears! You
are constantly hurt and depressed... No one
seems to understand how you feel because
everyone is scared to get close to you... You
long to be able to reach out and tell someone
everything, and all of your problems... But you
have no one to tell, or they just don't seem to
want to hear what you have to say. You've been
hurt many times that you don't seem to have any
tears left to shed, or if you do, they're an
endless river flowing... You've started to hide
and bottle up all or your problems and
feelings, hoping that maybe they just will go
away... You want company, but at the same time,
you're scared of it. Your sanctuary is your
room where you can just be alone and try to
throw away all of your aching pains. You're
dark and mysterious and people like you for
that reason. Even if you think you're all by
yourself in the dark, someone is always there
with you. Your special someone wants to admit
and show their feelings towards you, but
they're afraid of how you'll take it. Get out
more and enjoy life because, it is far too long
to frown your way through :)
